# List of places on the Victorian Heritage Register in the Rural City of Wangaratta

This is a list of places on the Victorian Heritage Register in the Rural City of Wangaratta in Victoria, Australia. The Victorian Heritage Register is maintained by the Heritage Council of Victoria.
The Victorian Heritage Register, as of 2021, lists the following fifteen state-registered places within the Rural City of Wangaratta:
